Class Description
CycleDetectedException
Thrown when an ordering cycle has been detected between two bindings.
DefaultPositionProvider
Gives a default position value for an OrderedBinding when it has no @Order annotation or when its Order.position() value is 0.
DuplicateIdentifiersException
Thrown when multiple bindings have the same identifier.
IdentifiedAs
Specifies that bindings targeting this class will be identified using the specified class.
MultibinderFinder
A simple helper to find multibinders and their bindings.
Order
Specifies the relative constraints on the position of bindings targeting this class in a Multibinder.
OrderedBinding
Represents an ordered binding with an identifier, its actual binding and its @Order annotation.
OrderedBinding.Builder
The builder for OrderedBinding.
OrderedBindingAnnotation
Specifies that the annotation is an identifier annotation that applies a OrderedBindingTransformer on classes where this annotation is present.
OrderedBindingTransformer
A function that transforms a OrderedBinding into another one, with different values, or not.
OrderedMultibinders
Sorts elements of Modules' multibinders according to their @Order annotation.
RedirectedByGenericParameter
Specifies that bindings targeting this class will be redirected using a specific generic parameter.
SortingConfiguration
Defines the configuration for sorting elements.
SortingConfiguration.Builder  
UnableToResolveClassAsBindingException
Thrown when a binding couldn't be resolved from the class of the @Order annotation.
UnresolvableClassHandling
Represents the behavior when a class in @Order can't be resolved as a binding.
